      "text": [
        " : \"مَا كَانَ مِنْ طَعَامٍ سَمَّيْتَ فِيهِ كَيْلاً فَلاَ يَصْلُحُ بَيْعُهُ مُجَازَفَةً هَذَا مِمَّا يُكْرَهُ مِنْ بَيْعِ اَلطَّعَامِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3829 - Al-Halabi narrated from Abu Abdullah (as):\n\"Any food for which a specific measure has been stated cannot be sold by estimation. This is among the practices that are disliked in selling food.\""
        ]
      }
